 Along with the rising popularity of Hanfu (traditional Han clothing), videos of 77-year-old Liu Weixiu dressed in Hanfu during daily life went viral on social media. Liu was a Beijing opera actress before her retirement. She wishes to promote traditional culture to younger generations, both at home and abroad. Video credit to "Hanfu Grandma" (Douyin#weixiunainai), posted on Chinese online video-sharing platform Douyin (the Chinese version of TikTok). (Source: Douyin)  